com.carteryagemann.AICS

Class AICSFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.carteryagemann.AICS.AICSFile

  • public class AICSFile
extends java.lang.Object
    An Android Intent Capture Session file. The file is organized into a fixed sized header followed by a chain of intent entries. Each intent logged in the file is represented as a header, containing meta information about the intent, and the intent itself.
